<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Fri, 01 Oct 2021 05:21:48 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>收貨後發現得 iPhone 13 Pro 吉盒，網上原價買 iPhone 中招</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/0u2kc0NtAc8/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 01 Oct 2021 05:20:02 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone 13 Pro]]></category><category><![CDATA[騙案]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1063490</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>有網民在 Facebook 群組「香港突發事故報料區及討論區」中發表帖文，表示一名賣家在 Facebook 出 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">有網民在 Facebook 群組「香港突發事故報料區及討論區」中發表帖文，表示一名賣家在 Facebook 出售 iPhone 13 Pro，在付足全款加運費後，竟然只收到一個空盒。受騙事主事後將對話紀錄放至群組，更表示「吹水嘅終生殘廢」，警戒大家小心受騙。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1063491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/EE1709C0-CBA0-49B9-AF3A-72BE231BC450-453x580.jpeg" alt="" width="453" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/EE1709C0-CBA0-49B9-AF3A-72BE231BC450-453x580.jpeg 453w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/EE1709C0-CBA0-49B9-AF3A-72BE231BC450-702x900.jpeg 702w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/EE1709C0-CBA0-49B9-AF3A-72BE231BC450-768x984.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/EE1709C0-CBA0-49B9-AF3A-72BE231BC450.jpeg 1058w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 453px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1063494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/92DDF5EB-BE1D-4140-ADB9-1BB6685CAE3C-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/92DDF5EB-BE1D-4140-ADB9-1BB6685CAE3C-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/92DDF5EB-BE1D-4140-ADB9-1BB6685CAE3C-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/92DDF5EB-BE1D-4140-ADB9-1BB6685CAE3C.jpeg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1063495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/6F78A888-75E7-4CF0-A74F-3DF8FBFC8DB7-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/6F78A888-75E7-4CF0-A74F-3DF8FBFC8DB7-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/6F78A888-75E7-4CF0-A74F-3DF8FBFC8DB7-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/6F78A888-75E7-4CF0-A74F-3DF8FBFC8DB7.jpeg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/HKGuy/permalink/1518753885162964/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Facebook 群組「香港突發事故報料區及討論區」</span></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">貼文中表示，事主原先是約定在地鐵交收，但需要先「落」1000 元作訂金，賣家更主動表示將會給事主一張「電子收據」。再得知賣家有送貨服務後，事主就另付 50 元給賣家作為運費，改為送貨服務。Lalamove 司機其後致電事主確認送貨地址，賣家亦在事主與司機掛斷電話後致電事主，表示她現在就將電話交給司機，還附送了不少配件。有見賣家誠意十足，事主亦十分相信賣家，立即將 iPhone 13 Pro 1TB 的款項 12699 元匯款給賣家。怎料事主在等候良久後仍未收到該有的 iPhone 13 Pro，想致電司機又發現沒有來電顯示。過一會兒事主收到來自 Lalamove 的短訊，稱包裹郵費需要到付 140 元，事主認為騙案與司機無關便將 140 元付清。但當事主一打開包裝，才發現這是這是一個空盒，無論是 iPhone 13 Pro 還是其配件，基本是什麼都沒有。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1063492" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/8E153BDD-0E9D-497F-A770-9A7526BB6F05-694x289.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="289" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/8E153BDD-0E9D-497F-A770-9A7526BB6F05-694x289.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/8E153BDD-0E9D-497F-A770-9A7526BB6F05-768x319.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/8E153BDD-0E9D-497F-A770-9A7526BB6F05.jpeg 991w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1063493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2079FCE9-47DE-4E83-947F-A59D6D993B8D-694x168.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="168" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2079FCE9-47DE-4E83-947F-A59D6D993B8D-694x168.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2079FCE9-47DE-4E83-947F-A59D6D993B8D-768x186.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2079FCE9-47DE-4E83-947F-A59D6D993B8D.jpeg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/HKGuy/permalink/1518753885162964/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Facebook 群組「香港突發事故報料區及討論區」</span></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">事件引起不少網民留言，笑稱事主是「交萬零蚊當學費」，亦有人替事主感到十分氣憤，認為被騙金額較大需報海關求助，起訴賣家訛騙又違反商品說明條例。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/HKGuy/permalink/1518753885162964/">Facebook</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwire</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
